										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[REUSE] CROWD_Enthralled_Kneeling, SCENE_MOO_Audience_Altar_Kneel_LOOP_PLYR, HUM_F_Rig_SCENE_GOB_Orpheus_SuppressedKneel_LOOP_PLYR, HUM_FS_Rig_SCENE_CRE_AstralPrison_Daisy_Kneel_LOOP_DSY, [CUSTOM] In his calm and powerful yet commanding posture, the PLYR softens his body language when they see how terrified the woman is. He shifts his expression, from malice to &quot;benevolence&quot;, as if he empathises and chooses “kindness” to rule. He slowly lifts his left hand up, fingers moving slowly yet surely, like a savior/saint's hand posture., [CUSTOM] From the default kneel pose, the WOMAN rocks her body, feeling terrified, trying to calm herself down. (something like fearful_kneel construction anim). She sees the PLYR noticing her and quickly averts her eyes away, with the context of &quot;oh crap! our eyes met! oh no no no no-&quot;    {Gwen Lee}" />
										</node>
