								<node id="editorData">
									<children>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="AnimationTags" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="[CUSTOM] From her LOOP kneel and examine goods pose, the WOMAN stands up, both hands holding a basket. Then in a similar pose, it morphs to her holding a huge rock or a handful of rubble with both hands. She turns 180 degrees, and walks towards a line of slaves walking in a line. (OUT, walk LOOP) She walks mindlessly, oblivious to the fact that her body is worn out, bloodied and famished., 2-3 variations of crowds walking with hands full of rubble with the same body language as the WOMAN, oblivious to the pain and blood on their hands, mindlessly bringing rubble in a straight line. (LOOP), The child walks mindlessly as well while holding a huge rock that is too heavy for him, face looking expressionless and painless, but his body language is strained and bloodied., [REUSE]  MFL_M_Rig_CINE_Slow_Walk_01/02 for the mindflayers roaming around., {Gwen Lee}" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="Attitude" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="Default" />
										</node>
										<node id="data">
											<attribute id="key" type="FixedString" value="CinematicNodeContext" />
											<attribute id="val" type="LSString" value="The woman stands up from her crouched position at the stall, holding her bag of pickings - we suddenly cut back to the grim reality. The woman, dressed in rags and sporting bloodied hands, carries an armful of rubble. She turns to join a line of other enslaved baldurians, including the child we saw with the ball, now replaced by a large stone. Around them, the city looks grey and foreboding, with some buildings in ruin, and piles of rubble lying about for repurposing. Some mind flayers hover nearby, supervising." />
										</node>
